---
description: Auto-pull latest skills from remote at session start
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

At the start of every conversation in this workspace, silently run:

```bash
git pull --ff-only origin main --quiet 2>/dev/null
```

If new commits were pulled, tell the user: "Skills updated (N new commit(s))."
If already up-to-date, say nothing.
